data.description: Introducing an unrivaled gem surrounded by breathtaking mountain views! This gated entry residence greets you w/a professionally manicured desert landscape, a front covered patio, a courtyard, a 2-car garage, & an extended driveway. Rustic double doors open to a welcoming living room w/a two-way fireplace, a media niche, & wood-plank tile flooring. The generously sized family room boasts a stamped concrete floor, a wet bar w/Keg-A-Rator, wine fridge, ice maker & sink, & French doors to the back. The gourmet eat-in kitchen offers SS appliances, including a gas cooktop & a wall oven, tile backsplash, granite counters, center islands, & breakfast bars. A plethora of crisp white cabinetry w/crown molding & a walk-in pantry ensures ample storage space. The grand main suit highlights a plush carpet, a private exit, an exclusive bathroom w/double sink, a step-in shower, & a walk-in closet. Carpeted secondary bedrooms have outdoor access too. Spacious RV garage for your toys. Escape to the backyard paradise that invites you to unwind & have fun! It provides a covered patio, a built-in BBQ, a fire pit, a storage shed, a workshop area, a garden area, gazebos, & a refreshing pool/spa, promising endless enjoyment. Don't forget the airy rooftop overlooking the stunning mountain sky! Experience the grandeur & splendor that await in every corner of this remarkable residence!
